short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to share the love of Ethan Bradberry on any website you are browsing using Google Chrome.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Listen to soothing sounds of Ethan Bradberry's voice as he tells you "I'm Ethan Bradberry". It helps calm the nerves and put you into a different state. I hope you like it! Video Credit to: NukeDuck on Youtube. Go subscribe!
